ws.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/special_report/1998/03/98/russian_mafia/70485.stm| archive-date=April 6, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"unreported cases\">{{cite web| url=http://www.unreportedcases.com/mafia-crimes/russian-mafia-mafia-crimes/the-russian-mafia-part-three| title=The Russian Mafia \u2013 Part Three| publisher=UnreportedCases.com| date=March 11, 2011| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121027085707/http://www.unreportedcases.com/mafia-crimes/russian-mafia-mafia-crimes/the-russian-mafia-part-three| archive-date=October 27, 2012| url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ITAR-TASS\">{{cite web| url=http://www.itar-tass.com/en/c154/219594.html| title=Leader of Orekhovskaya gang sentenced to life in jail| publisher=ITAR-TASS| date=June 9, 2011| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603033159/http://www.itar-tass.com/en/c154/219594.html| archive-date=June 3, 2013| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"kyivpost\">{{cite web| url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/russia-and-former-soviet-union/russian-crime-gang-leader-gets-life-in-jail.html#.UAc19WGe4pI| title=Russian crime gang leader gets life in jail| work=Kyiv Post| date=September 7, 2011| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527063925/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/russia-and-former-soviet-union/russian-crime-gang-leader-gets-life-in-jail.html#.UAc19WGe4pI| archive-date=May 27, 2015| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"fas.org\">{{cite web| url=https://fas.org/irp/world/para/docs/rusorg3.htm| title=Russian Organized Crime| publisher=fas.org| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120620164730/http://www.fas.org/irp/world/para/docs/rusorg3.htm| archive-date=June 20, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"most powerful\">{{cite web| url=http://english.pravda.ru/russia/politics/07-11-2011/119544-russian_mafia-0/| title=Russian mafia most powerful in the world?| last=Sinelnikov| first=Mikhail| publisher=Pravda.ru| date=July 11, 2011| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120711235319/http://english.pravda.ru/russia/politics/07-11-2011/119544-russian_mafia-0/| archive-date=July 11, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"hetq.am\">{{cite web| url=http://hetq.am/eng/news/11834/obama-calls-brothers-circle-a-national-security-threatbut-who-are-they?.html| title=Obama Calls \"Brothers' Circle\" a National Security Threat...But Who Are They?| publisher=Hetq.am| date=March 14, 2012| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318200323/http://hetq.am/eng/news/11834/obama-calls-brothers-circle-a-national-security-threatbut-who-are-they?.html| archive-date=March 18, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"treasury\">{{cite web| url=http://www.treasury.gov/press-center/press-releases/Pages/tg1605.aspx| title=Treasury Designates Brothers' Circle Members| publisher=[[US Department of Treasury]]| date=June 6, 2012| accessdate=July 19, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120616103334/http://www.treasury.gov/press-center/press-releases/Pages/tg1605.aspx| archive-date=June 16, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"early US crime\">{{cite news| url=https://www.nytimes.com/1989/06/04/nyregion/soviet-emigre-mob-outgrows-brooklyn-and-fear-spreads.html?src=pm| title=Soviet Emigre Mob Outgrows Brooklyn, and Fear Spreads| author=Ralph Blumenthal, Celestine Bohlen| work=[[New York Times]]| date=June 4, 1989| accessdate=July 20, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605234102/http://www.nytimes.com/1989/06/04/nyregion/soviet-emigre-mob-outgrows-brooklyn-and-fear-spreads.html?src=pm| archive-date=June 5, 2013| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RICO Act\">{{cite web| url=http://concept.journals.villanova.edu/article/view/312/275| title=Ideas Shoot Bullets: How the RICO Act Became a Potent Weapon in the War Against Organized Crime| last=Gordon| first=Mark| acces