n.rian.ru/russia/20090423/121263983.html| title=Miami becomes 'Little Moscow': FBI says Russian mob eclipses Italian Mafia in South Florida| work=[[Daily Mail]]| date=June 1, 2011| accessdate=July 20, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130612184617/http://en.rian.ru/russia/20090423/121263983.html| archive-date=June 12, 2013| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"WikiLeaks\">{{cite web| url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-11893886| title=Wikileaks: Russia branded 'mafia state' in cables| publisher=BBC News| date=December 2, 2010| accessdate=July 20, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121029015213/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-11893886| archive-date=October 29, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"extend sanctions\">{{cite web| url=http://www.courthousenews.com/2012/07/20/48589.htm| title=War on International Criminals Continues| publisher=BBC News| date=July 20, 2012| accessdate=July 21, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530162024/http://www.courthousenews.com/2012/07/20/48589.htm| archive-date=May 30, 2013| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Mogilevich Organization\">{{cite web| url=http://www.larryjkolb.com/file/docs/fbimogilevich.pdf| title=Semion Mogilevich Organization: Eurasian Organized Crime| publisher=[[FBI]]| date=August 1996| accessdate=July 21, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121210024412/http://www.larryjkolb.com/file/docs/fbimogilevich.pdf| archive-date=December 10, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n}}\n\n==Sources==\n* {{cite web|url=http://web.wm.edu/so/monitor/issues/07-1/4-hatcher.htm|title=The Russian mafia and its impact on the Russian economy|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227130753/http://web.wm.edu/so/monitor/issues/07-1/4-hatcher.htm|archivedate=2013-12-27}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.uexpress.com/georgie-anne-geyer/1997/9/30/russian-mafia-controls-economy-and-politics|title=Russian mafia controls economy and politics}}\