ail| publisher=ITAR-TASS| date=June 9, 2011| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603033159/http://www.itar-tass.com/en/c154/219594.html| archive-date=June 3, 2013| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"kyivpost\">{{cite web| url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/russia-and-former-soviet-union/russian-crime-gang-leader-gets-life-in-jail.html#.UAc19WGe4pI| title=Russian crime gang leader gets life in jail| work=Kyiv Post| date=September 7, 2011| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527063925/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/russia-and-former-soviet-union/russian-crime-gang-leader-gets-life-in-jail.html#.UAc19WGe4pI| archive-date=May 27, 2015| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"fas.org\">{{cite web| url=https://fas.org/irp/world/para/docs/rusorg3.htm| title=Russian Organized Crime| publisher=fas.org| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120620164730/http://www.fas.org/irp/world/para/docs/rusorg3.htm| archive-date=June 20, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"most powerful\">{{cite web| url=http://english.pravda.ru/russia/politics/07-11-2011/119544-russian_mafia-0/| title=Russian mafia most powerful in the world?| last=Sinelnikov| first=Mikhail| publisher=Pravda.ru| date=July 11, 2011| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120711235319/http://english.pravda.ru/russia/politics/07-11-2011/119544-russian_mafia-0/| archive-date=July 11, 2012| url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"hetq.am\">{{cite web| url=http://hetq.am/eng/news/11834/obama-calls-brothers-circle-a-national-security-threatbut-who-are-they?.html| title=Obama Calls \"Brothers' Circle\" a National Security Threat...But Who Are They?| publisher=Hetq.am| date=March 14, 2012| accessdate=July 18, 2012| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318200323/http://hetq.am/eng/news/11834/obama-calls-brothers-circle-a-national-security-threatbut-who-are-they?.html| archive-date=M